  "body_html": "<div class=\"si-calc-page\">\n  <div class=\"si-container\" style=\"max-width:900px;\">\n    <div class=\"si-calc-header si-reveal\">\n      <span class=\"si-badge\" style=\"background:var(--si-accent-light);color:var(--si-accent);\">4 outils gratuits</span>\n      <h1>Outils de simulation immobiliere</h1>\n      <p>ScoreImmo met a disposition des futurs acheteurs et investisseurs une suite d'outils gratuits pour preparer votre projet immobilier. Frais de notaire, capacite d'emprunt, mensualites, rendement locatif : simulez chaque etape de votre parcours d'achat en quelques clics. Pas d'inscription requise, pas de pub, des calculs precis et a jour.</p>\n    </div>\n    <div class=\"si-calc-hub-grid\">\n      <a href=\"/pages/calculateur-frais-de-notaire\" class=\"si-calc-hub-card si-reveal si-reveal-delay-1\">\n        <div class=\"si-calc-hub-card-icon\">\n          <svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" viewbox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"1.5\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\"><path d=\"M14 2H6a2 2 0 0 0-2 2v16a2 2 0 0 0 2 2h12a2 2 0 0 0 2-2V8z\"></path><polyline points=\"14 2 14 8 20 8\"></polyline><line x1=\"16\" y1=\"13\" x2=\"8\" y2=\"13\"></line><line x1=\"16\" y1=\"17\" x2=\"8\" y2=\"17\"></line><polyline points=\"10 9 9 9 8 9\"></polyline></svg>\n        </div>\n        <div class=\"si-calc-hub-card-title\">Frais de notaire</div>\n        <div class=\"si-calc-hub-card-desc\">Calculez le montant exact de vos frais de notaire selon le departement, le type de bien et le prix d'achat.</div>\n        <span class=\"si-calc-hub-card-tag\">101 departements</span>\n      </a>\n      <a href=\"/pages/calculateur-capacite-emprunt\" class=\"si-calc-hub-card si-reveal si-reveal-delay-2\">\n        <div class=\"si-calc-hub-card-icon\">\n          <svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" viewbox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"1.5\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\"><rect x=\"1\" y=\"4\" width=\"22\" height=\"16\" rx=\"2\" ry=\"2\"></rect><line x1=\"1\" y1=\"10\" x2=\"23\" y2=\"10\"></line></svg>\n        </div>\n        <div class=\"si-calc-hub-card-title\">Capacite d'emprunt</div>\n        <div class=\"si-calc-hub-card-desc\">Estimez le montant maximum que vous pouvez emprunter en fonction de vos revenus et de la duree souhaitee.</div>\n        <span class=\"si-calc-hub-card-tag\">Norme HCSF 35%</span>\n      </a>\n      <a href=\"/pages/calculateur-mensualite-credit\" class=\"si-calc-hub-card si-reveal si-reveal-delay-3\">\n        <div class=\"si-calc-hub-card-icon\">\n          <svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" viewbox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"1.5\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\"><line x1=\"12\" y1=\"1\" x2=\"12\" y2=\"23\"></line><path d=\"M17 5H9.5a3.5 3.5 0 0 0 0 7h5a3.5 3.5 0 0 1 0 7H6\"></path></svg>\n        </div>\n        <div class=\"si-calc-hub-card-title\">Mensualite de credit</div>\n        <div class=\"si-calc-hub-card-desc\">Simulez vos mensualites avec le detail capital, interets et assurance, plus le tableau d'amortissement.</div>\n        <span class=\"si-calc-hub-card-tag\">Amortissement detaille</span>\n      </a>\n      <a href=\"/pages/calculateur-rendement-locatif\" class=\"si-calc-hub-card si-reveal si-reveal-delay-4\">\n        <div class=\"si-calc-hub-card-icon\">\n          <svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" viewbox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"1.5\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\"><polyline points=\"22 12 18 12 15 21 9 3 6 12 2 12\"></polyline></svg>\n        </div>\n        <div class=\"si-calc-hub-card-title\">Rendement locatif</div>\n        <div class=\"si-calc-hub-card-desc\">Evaluez la rentabilite brute, nette et nette-nette de votre investissement locatif, regime fiscal inclus.</div>\n        <span class=\"si-calc-hub-card-tag\">Brut / Net / Net-net</span>\n      </a>\n    </div>\n    <!-- STEPPER -->\n    <div class=\"si-stepper si-reveal\">\n      <div class=\"si-step\">\n        <div class=\"si-step-number\">1</div>\n        <div>\n          <div class=\"si-step-title\">Capacite d'emprunt</div>\n          <div class=\"si-step-desc\">Combien puis-je emprunter ?</div>\n        </div>\n      </div>\n      <div class=\"si-step\">\n        <div class=\"si-step-number\">2</div>\n        <div>\n          <div class=\"si-step-title\">Mensualite de credit</div>\n          <div class=\"si-step-desc\">Combien vais-je payer par mois ?</div>\n        </div>\n      </div>\n      <div class=\"si-step\">\n        <div class=\"si-step-number\">3</div>\n        <div>\n          <div class=\"si-step-title\">Frais de notaire</div>\n          <div class=\"si-step-desc\">Quel est le cout total de l'achat ?</div>\n        </div>\n      </div>\n      <div class=\"si-step\">\n        <div class=\"si-step-number\">4</div>\n        <div>\n          <div class=\"si-step-title\">Rendement locatif</div>\n          <div class=\"si-step-desc\">Est-ce un bon investissement ?</div>\n        </div>\n      </div>\n    </div>\n    <div style=\"text-align:center;margin-top:2.5rem;\" class=\"si-reveal\">\n      <p style=\"font-family:var(--si-font-body);font-size:0.9375rem;color:var(--si-muted-foreground);margin-bottom:1rem;max-width:36rem;margin-left:auto;margin-right:auto;line-height:1.65;\">Ces outils vous donnent les bases. Pour une analyse complete d'une annonce immobiliere : prix au m², estimation, points de vigilance, tendances du quartier. Essayez ScoreImmo, c'est gratuit pour votre premiere analyse.</p>\n      <a href=\"https://app.score-immo.fr\" class=\"si-btn si-btn-primary si-btn-primary-lg si-cta-glow\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">\n        Analyser une annonce\n        <svg class=\"si-arrow\" xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" viewbox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\"><line x1=\"5\" y1=\"12\" x2=\"19\" y2=\"12\"></line><polyline points=\"12 5 19 12 12 19\"></polyline></svg>\n      </a>\n    </div>\n  </div>\n</div>\n<script>\n(function(){\n  var obs = new IntersectionObserver(function(entries){\n    entries.forEach(function(e){\n      if(e.isIntersecting){e.target.classList.add('si-revealed');obs.unobserve(e.target);}\n    });\n  },{threshold:0.1});\n  document.querySelectorAll('.si-reveal').forEach(function(el){obs.observe(el);});\n})();\n</script>",
